{
  "texts": [
    "Filings An exhaustive scrape of the EDGAR SEC database from 1993 to 2023 provided detailed records of accurate business, financial and accounting information from official filings.",
    "This dataset, exclusively in English, added substantial depth, allowing for analysis of historical market regulatory impacts and corporate financial maneuvers.",
    "Company Websites and Social Media Further data were obtained from the top 5000 company websites and their social media presence on platforms like Facebook, Instagram, and Reddit.",
    "This dataset provided direct corporate communications and captured broader market sentiments and public perceptions, notably through an extensive scrape of the r/WallStreetBets Reddit community.",
    "We started of gathering various text corpora shown in table 1, resulting in a dataset consisting of 2.9B documents."
  ]
}